Skills.Name: Time to Shine!
Skills.Description: Raises own DEF by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 10s. Further recovers HP by <color=red>{1}%</color> of ATK. Inflicts Provoke on all enemies for 15s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises own DEF, recovers HP. Inflicts Provoke on all enemies

Skills.Name: Beauty of Nature
Skills.Description: Inflicts Stun on single enemy with highest ATK for 3s. Further inflicts 3-hit DMG (<color=red>{1}%</color> + <color=red>{2}%</color> + <color=red>{3}%</color>). Shields DMG (<color=red>{4}%</color> of skill user's ATK) of all Shadow Garden allies for 15s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts Stun and DMG on single enemy. Shields DMG of all Shadow Garden allies

Skills.Name: New Year Kagura Dance
Skills.Description: Shields DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> of skill user's ATK) on all allies for 15s. Further raises ATK by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 15s and Speed by <color=red>{2}%</color> for 15s if Shadow Garden. Recovers own HP by <color=red>{3}%</color> of ATK.
Skills.ShortDescription: Shields DMG of all allies. Further raises ATK and Speed if Shadow Garden. Recovers own HP

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Reduces DMG Received for all allies by <color=red>5.00%-40.00%</color> for 5s according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription: Reduces DMG Received for all allies. Inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Shared Silence
Skills.Description: Each time DMG is received, recovers own HP by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK up to 3 times (CT 3s). Further shields DMG (<color=red>{1}%</color> of skill user's ATK) for 15s up to 3 times. (CT 3s)
Skills.ShortDescription: Each time DMG is received, recovers own HP and shields DMG up to 3 times
